    "description": "两只手！乐趣无穷<br>&quot;两只手的蛋&quot;就是一个普通的鸡蛋......只不过它有两只手！<br>你还可以变成蛋，跑、跳和游泳！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/0c2175c916a2497c72fb87efd5db05ef.poster.avif?t=1754582231\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/0c2175c916a2497c72fb87efd5db05ef.webm?t=1754582231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/0c2175c916a2497c72fb87efd5db05ef.mp4?t=1754582231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>您只需使用控制器上的两个摇杆。<br>当你倾斜摇杆时，手会随着摇杆一起移动。<br>如果你的手碰到地面，你就会跳起来。<br>你还可以做各种动作，比如像轮胎一样旋转手部来行走。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>阶段模式</strong></h2>在 4 个世界（草地、冰雪、水域、火山）中各有 6 个阶段<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/cd691801d99c7dd88fb2c06887f81c62.poster.avif?t=1754582231\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/cd691801d99c7dd88fb2c06887f81c62.webm?t=1754582231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/cd691801d99c7dd88fb2c06887f81c62.mp4?t=1754582231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>迷你游戏模式</strong></h2>2-4 人模式<br>在早期访问开始时有两种类型。<br><br><strong>相扑</strong><br>击败对手的模式！<br>最后剩下的蛋就是赢家！!<br><br><strong>排球</strong><br>使用蛋形球进行排球比赛！<br>球的种类和球场有很多。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于现场直播</strong></h2>请将本网站用于商业或非商业目的。",
